It really informative and I'm just trying to find the third video of Josh Carlton

The Book by Carlton is I.M.O. a must as well as his DVD series. I believe everyone will benefit from reading the Book & Watching the DVD'S. see my review of his book.

He goes over a lot in the DVD'S. such as needle selection, why he tattoos Mag first. Machine Set Up's, Color Theories..

I highly. Recommend these  DVD'S.

Take Care, Bill Kearney. :-)

AMAZING VIDEO!!! So Informative!!! No matter what your skill level, you can't watch this video without learning something! Josh Carlton has been one of my favorite tattoo artist for a while now and I am very happy to have these videos to help sharpen my skills as a tattoo artist and broaden my arsenal of artistic techniques... And at this price, if you were considering purchasing this video, do yourself the favor and buy it right away...
i love Joshuas work so i like watching all he does. Great stuff and great price. Good buy wasn't messed up.
